Job Description
CLIFFSOL BPO is looking for Experienced Appointment Setting for US & Canada. Job is related to lead Generation and appointment setting with US business. We are looking for Young, Energetic, Talented, Sharp Individuals Males and Females who can speak Fluent English confidently. CLIFFSOL BPO is giving Free Call Center Training with a guaranteed job!!! Attractive Basic Salary + Commissions+ Performance Incentives
Job Specification
The candidates must have the following:1. American accent/ Neutral accent2. Should be able to speak English fluently with full confidence3. International Call Center Experience will be added advantage4. Must have strong interpersonal skills5. Must have strong selling skills 6. Must be available for work during Night Shift (9pm - 6am)
